Erik von Detten https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erik_von_Detten 0 Erik Thomas von Detten (born October 3, 1982) is a former American actor. He is known for his roles in Escape to Witch Mountain, Toy Story, Brink!, The Princess Diaries, Complete Savages, and So Weird.
